## About this package

This package provides ONNX Runtime v${EMGU_ONNXRUNTIME_VERSION}.

This package provides the native ONNX Runtime dependency for EMGU software libraries, including the CUDA and TensorRT execution provider libraries when the build includes GPU support.

For for information, please visit
<${NUGET_EMGU_URL}/wiki>

